<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٣٨٤ - ح ز ق]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تحزَّقَ يتحزَّق، تحزُّقًا، فهو مُتحزِّق<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تحزَّق الشَّيءُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - تجمَّع وانضغط <span class="c1">"تحزَّقت قدمُه في الحذاء"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - ضاق وقصر <span class="c1">"تحزَّق الثّوبُ"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>